> @patronovski what does the code of producer side looks like? What is the key for each message?

Hi, below is the code for the producer:

`@Slf4j
@RestController
@RequestMapping(value = "/customers")
public class CustomerController {

  @Autowired
  private Producer<Customer> producer;
  
  @GetMapping(value = "/create/{id}")
  public void create(@PathVariable String id) throws PulsarClientException {
    Faker faker = new Faker();
    producer.newMessage()
        .key(id)
        .value(Customer.builder()
            .id(id)
            .firstName(faker.name().firstName())
            .lastName(faker.name().lastName())
            .address(faker.address().streetAddress())
            .postal(faker.address().zipCode())
            .city(faker.address().city())
            .country(faker.address().country())
            .credit(100)
            .build())
        .send();
  }

}`

